# create a cleaning fucntion
def clean_text(x):
    x = x.replace('$','')
    x = x.replace(',','')
    x = x.replace('-','')
    x = x.replace(' ','')
    x = pd.to_numeric(x)
    return x
df['Medication Revenue'] = df['Medication Revenue'].apply(clean_text)
df.head()

merge.head()
